                                            <h2 class="ez-toc-section" id="man-khoroja-fi-tholabul-ilmi-fahuwa-fi-sabilillah-hatta-yarjijelaskan-isi-kandungan-dari-hadits-diatas-khoroja-fiil-madhi-atau-dihiris">
                            14. man khoroja fi tholabul ilmi fahuwa fi sabilillah hatta yarji
